dct_title_s: Map of South Australia, showing public works under the engineer-in-chief's department
dct_description_sm: Surveyor Generals Office, Adelaide. A. Vaughan, Photo-lithographer (247).
Shows railways with stations, roads (including those under repair), water districts and trusts, lighthouses, jetties and wharves, water supplies on stock routes, waterways, towns.
